Getting fixtures
----------------

In order to get fixtures from Gerrit you need to be able to clone via SSH with
your current user or configure SSH so it sets the right user, in my case:

    Host gerrit.devcl.am.ntt.eu
    User rafael.duran

Create ruby/puppet project
--------------------------

Just type something like this:

    jenkins create $project.name \
        --rubies ruby-1.8.7-p374,ruby-1.9.3-p484,ruby-2.0.0-p247,ruby-2.1.0 \
        --no-build \
        --scm ssh://jenkins@gerrit.devcl.am.ntt.eu:29418/$project.name.git \
        --scm-branches ** --template rubygem
